X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/Los_Angeles
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:NO KINGS Yolo County
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260328T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260328T130000
UID:14988e9fc10afd199af077889110ce19@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/NK3_16x9-2_20260214005634658774.png
DESCRIPTION:On March 28th\, we will rise up\, take to the streets\, and sa
 y it loud: No Thrones! No Crowns! No Kings! We’re not watching history h
 appen—we’re making it. Yolo residents from across the county will gath
 er together at beautiful RiverWalk Park in West Sacramento to fight for ou
 r democracy. At 11:30 there will be a brief program before we march en mas
 se at noon across the majestic Tower Bridge to the State Capitol where we 
 join with other groups coming from across the Sacramento area. The preside
 nt 
LOCATION:RiverWalk Park\, 651 2nd St\, West Sacramento\, CA\, 95605
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisibleyolo/event/901224/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Yolo (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Voter Registration Training: No Kings Yolo Democracy Fair
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260328T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260328T120000
UID:d821eb7a58c17eb387d82c31a25470ae@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/voter%20regsitration_20260318142541764393.png
DESCRIPTION:If you're ready to do more than protest\, join us at the State
 s Win Yolo table at the Democracy Fair before the No Kings Yolo rally and 
 walk. No experience necessary. We'll start with an inspiring 15-minute tra
 ining and then practice by approaching rally attendees. Every Democrat we 
 register breathes new life into our dreams for a better world. And all it 
 takes is talking to people and filling out a short form. We'll have clipbo
 ards\, forms\, pens\, and stickers! Just bring a little water\, sunscreen
LOCATION:River Walk Park\, 651 2nd St\, West Sacramento\, CA\, 95605
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/stateswinyolo/event/923319/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Yolo (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
