DESCRIPTION:Join local activists to take action for change! Fight the Trum
 p regime by joining our Woodland Activist Circle. We are using the tenets 
 of Indivisible to guide us. This is your forum do something to stop the Tr
 ump regime while building community here in Woodland. This month we are me
 eting at the spacious and well-appointed community room at the County Libr
 ary in Yolo\, California. The hamlet of Yolo is just a short six-mile driv
 e up Interstate 5. Bring some food to share for a social hour at 5:00
LOCATION:Yolo Branch Library Community Room\, 37750 Sacramento St. Yolo CA
 \, Woodland\, CA\, 95695
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisibleyolo/event/774543/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Yolo (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
